Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the unfamiliar goat who thought Wolffy was going to eat him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,escaped Wolf Fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran into Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Weslie recognize this skittish little goat or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve finally found my notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this notebook yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it even has my name,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“Marky.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don’t lose it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are my two rocket blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They were tucked in right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I might have accidentally lost them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make sure to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That wolf must have forgotten about me by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world are my blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do the blueprints look like, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My yellow blueprints are about this big,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have purple-colored drawings of rocket designs on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprints can’t just have flown out by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was the naughty bear cubs who took the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This goat is working so hard to help me get back my blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His selfless figure appears to grow larger and larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to get to it if it’s all the way up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s time for another miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the Creaky Squeaky Flying Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just run while pulling the two strings on the sides, and you’ll fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I knocked down the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,10,,—Let’s go home.　—It’s those bear cubs throwing paper airplanes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blueprint is still in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it’ll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn’t possibly fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, your invention is actually pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the second person to encourage my innovations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what’s your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Marky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let’s go find the rest of your blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll ask my friend to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll find them faster that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie’s friend must be a very talented goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve been looking for you, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You left without saying a word last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him, Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s the little goat I was telling you about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s kind of a long story, so I’ll tell you more inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he faint again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His health is quite poor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,…And that’s what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I accidentally lost his rocket blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you help me find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll just use my satellite to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll take a photo of every corner of the grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, we’ll take our time and hunt through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} many?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A familiar ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and familiar sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie? What’s he doing with a wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have any tools that could be of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking a wolf for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look at my Extendable Goat Catcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“Goat Catcher?”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! With this, I’ll be able to catch them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won’t lose them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s going to use that thing to catch goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie is one with the wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d better get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell all of Goats’ Village
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that Weslie is a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to take my notebook again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I run so fast for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll just go back and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He left again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His notebook is still here, so he can’t be far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Marky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you go outside, Marky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, I got my notebook back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky, where are you going with your notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The last blueprint is in a canyon near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys are using the blueprints to trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun conspiring with the wolves, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That little goat disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hear me, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not listening to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to lose our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky, please come out. Let’s talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that we’re all called Marky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t matter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that we’re friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So you weren’t talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,my blueprint? It really {\i1}is{\i0} down the canyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I wrong about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Marky,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the stuff I just said was for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from the canyon edge, Marky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to us, you little goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,—Marky!　—You little goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We warned you that it’s dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I might as well get the blueprint, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll slowly fly to the ground now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So thirsty…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How come it’s paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,—Marky!　—You little goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m coming to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll leave Marky to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,little goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d rather fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re not going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They sacrificed themselves to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they weren’t so evil after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolf-something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are over here? But over there—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is {\i1}Wolffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I’m not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That hug just now was to thank you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I’m keeping my distance now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because you, Weslie, are helping wolves catch goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly which village are you from, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you not know that I don’t eat goats anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wanted to eat you, you’d have been gone a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy is friends with us goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what did you want the “Goat Catcher” for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant using it to catch the blueprint
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so it wouldn’t get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to eat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have eaten me while I was asleep yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the name of this thing made me think that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you’re
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,still catching goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I’ll change the name of it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to Green Green Grassland’s cutest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so much that even the goats think so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“Little Cutesy!”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I was wrong about you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s play together again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going home now. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So which village is that kid from, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
